            "pathId": -516411774274467357,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エイシンフラッシュ",
            "enName": "Eishin Flash",
            "jpText": "このままでは予定に大幅な遅滞が発生……\n想定外でした。一体どうすれば――",
            "enText": "If we don't, there will be a significant \ndelay in our schedule… We didn't expect \nthis. What can we do to…",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いっそ自分で作るのはどうだろう",
                    "enText": "Why don't you make your own?",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "いっそ自分で作るのはどうかな",
                    "enText": "Why don't you make your own?",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "取り扱ってる店を他に探すのはどうだろう",
                    "enText": "How about finding another \nshop that sells it?",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "取り扱ってる店を他に探すのはどうかな",
                    "enText": "I'm not sure if you can find another \nshop that carries it.",
