        {
            "jpName": "エイシンフラッシュ",
            "enName": "Eishin Flash",
            "jpText": "無いなら作ればいい。幸い、味も鮮明に\n思い出せるほど此方には通っています。",
            "enText": "If you don't have it, you can make it. \nFortunately, I've been coming here long \nenough to remember the taste very clearly.",
