            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エイシンフラッシュ",
            "enName": "Eishin Flash",
            "jpText": "父と母のシュトレンのレシピを元にして、\n近似した風味を再現できるかもしれません。",
            "enText": "You may be able to recreate a similar \nflavour based on your father and mother's \nstollen recipe.",
